Privacy Commitment:

CrampPanchayat is committed to user privacy and data protection. This software:

1. Does not collect or store personal identifying information
2. Uses emoji-based anonymous profiles for user identity
3. Stores data locally by default (offline-first)
4. Provides optional cloud sync with anonymous identifiers
5. Allows users to export and delete all their data
6. Implements privacy-by-design principles
7. Complies with GDPR and similar privacy regulations

The developers and contributors of CrampPanchayat respect menstrual health privacy
and cultural sensitivity. This software is designed to empower users while
protecting their personal information.

For privacy questions or concerns, contact: privacy@cramppanchayat.com
